# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:16
translate chinese welchs1_a32046bb:

    # sst "Not really. I mean, I don't keep in touch with them."
    sst "其实倒也不是。我是说，我跟她们没什么联系。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:17
translate chinese welchs1_e9cca3d8:

    # sst "They are very different from me."
    sst "她们跟我完全不一样。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:18
translate chinese welchs1_90640fc0:

    # sst "But I do still talk to my ex-husband's family pretty often."
    sst "但我确实还经常跟我前夫的家人联系。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:19
translate chinese welchs1_b8887ab1:

    # pc "You were married?"
    pc "你结过婚？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:24
translate chinese welchmarried_c27601eb:

    # sst "Oh yeah. Right out of high school. Lasted about two years."
    sst "哦，是啊。刚高中毕业就结的。维持了大概两年。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:25
translate chinese welchmarried_d6a910a0:

    # sst "But he was controlling and emotionally abusive..."
    sst "但他很控制欲强，还对我进行情感虐待……"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:27
translate chinese welchmarried_6cf00ff4:

    # sst "So, I left his ass."
    sst "所以，我甩了他。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:29
translate chinese welchmarried_5314674d:

    # sst "The whole thing made me stronger though. I don't think I'd be the same person today if I hadn't married that asshole."
    sst "不过那段经历让我变得更坚强了。要不是嫁给那个混蛋，我觉得现在的我不会是这样的人。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:31
translate chinese welchmarried_a405651c:

    # sst "Plus, I got a pretty sweet house out of the divorce."
    sst "而且，离婚时我还分到了一栋挺不错的房子。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:32
translate chinese welchmarried_7acc68d6:

    # pc "Hey, that's cool."
    pc "嘿，那挺不错的。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:34
translate chinese welchmarried_5d0c7d8f:

    # sst "His parents and I always got along."
    sst "我和他父母一直相处得很好。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:35
translate chinese welchmarried_c3bfaae0:

    # sst "They helped me a lot when I was leaving him, and we still go out for dinner once a month or so."
    sst "我离开他的时候，他们帮了我大忙，现在我们大概每个月还会一起出去吃顿饭。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:37
translate chinese welchmarried_9b93bf6c:

    # sst "So, I guess I took his family in the divorce too! Hah!"
    sst "所以，我感觉离婚时连他的家人也一并“娶”进来了！哈哈！"

# game/Scenes/Welch/WelchConversations/welchs1.rpy:38
translate chinese welchmarried_201d5764:

    # pc "Nice."
    pc "真不错。"

